excerpt: Cozy, high-end hotel eatery celebrated for its genteel ambiance & inventive New American cooking.
detail_description: Cafe Marquesa is a charming and upscale restaurant located just off Duval Street in Key West's historic district. Despite its central location, the restaurant offers a serene atmosphere with a lush garden providing privacy from the bustling tourist area. The 50-seat interior exudes simplicity and elegance, perfectly complementing the menu of reinvented classic dishes that offer a familiar yet unique dining experience. The starters, including shrimp and grits with andouille sausage and country ham, are highly recommended.
name: Cafe Marquesa
address: 600 Fleming St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Traditional Cuban home cooking & housemade sangria in a casual, family-friendly setting.
detail_description: El Siboney Restaurant is a casual, family-friendly spot known for its traditional Cuban home cooking and housemade sangria. Key West offers a diverse culinary scene with influences from around the world due to its immigrant culture. Visitors can enjoy a mix of flavors including Cuban, Mediterranean, Caribbean, and Italian cuisine.
name: El Siboney Restaurant
address: 900 Catherine St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Iconic landmark for Floridian-Caribbean cuisine & key lime pie, with a funky setting.
detail_description: Blue Heaven is a renowned dining spot in Key West, known for its iconic Floridian-Caribbean cuisine and delectable key lime pie. The restaurant boasts a funky setting in a shady backyard, offering classic cooking and flavors. It's one of the top 10 restaurants noted by Conde Nast Traveler, alongside other unique dining establishments in the area.
name: Blue Heaven
address: 729 Thomas St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Simple eatery offering crab cake & shrimp salad sandwiches, plus fried fish & grilled lobster tail.
detail_description: Eaton Street Seafood Market, located in a converted old gas station, offers an array of fresh seafood options. Whether you're looking to cook at home or indulge in a delicious meal on-site, this casual eatery has you covered. The menu features a variety of sandwiches including crab cake and shrimp salad, as well as fried fish and grilled lobster tail. Additionally, the market provides fresh fish to go for those who prefer cooking at home.
name: Eaton Street Seafood Market
address: 801 Eaton St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Veteran Cuban eatery draws crowds with rustic look, live music & Mallory Square sunset celebration.
detail_description: El Meson De Pepe's Restaurant & Bar is a beloved Cuban eatery located in the vibrant Old Town neighborhood of Key West, near Mallory Square. With over 30 years of history, this family-owned establishment is dedicated to preserving the Cuban Conch Heritage. The founder, Pepe Diaz, hails from Yaguajay, Cuba and has crafted a menu featuring authentic Cuban dishes such as roasted pork tostones rellenos and cayo hueso Cuban sandwich.
name: El Meson De Pepe's Restaurant & Bar
address: 410 Wall St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Offbeat eatery in a driftwood shack doling out fried fish, conch fritters, hot dogs & sandwiches.
detail_description: B.O.'s Fish Wagon is a quirky seafood shack located in Key West, known for its laid-back atmosphere and delicious food. The eatery gained recognition from the NY Times and even caught the attention of Bobby Flay. The menu offers a variety of seafood dishes with a local twist, perfect for grabbing on-the-go or enjoying at the open-air eatery adorned with eclectic decor.
name: B.O.'s Fish Wagon
address: 801 Caroline St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Tiny, husband-&-wife-run food stand serving eclectic, inventive takes on tacos, burritos & burgers.
detail_description: Garbo's Grill @ Hanks is a small, family-run food stand offering unique twists on tacos, burritos, and burgers. Despite its unassuming appearance as a shiny airstream camper parked behind a bar, it has gained popularity in Key West and even attracted the attention of Guy Fieri from Diners Drive Ins and Dives. The restaurant was born out of the owners' dream to open a place in Key West but faced challenges due to high lease prices for traditional spaces.
name: Garbo's Grill @ Hanks!
address: 409 Caroline St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Upscale restaurant with sea views, outdoor dining & a menu of contemporary cuisine.
detail_description: Latitudes - Sunset Key Cottages is an upscale restaurant with stunning sea views and outdoor dining. It's part of the Sunset Key Cottages hotel and boasts a colonial villa ambiance inspired by the Gulf of Mexico. The menu features contemporary cuisine, including traditional items like avocado toasts, egg benedicts, main lobster roll, cubano sandwiches, and swordfish linguini. Guests can also indulge in the must-try dessert - Key Lime Pie.
name: Latitudes - Sunset Key Cottages
address: 245 Front St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Charming seaside eatery with open-air patios serving up a menu of Latin American-style small plates.
detail_description: Hot Tin Roof Restaurant is a charming seaside eatery located in the Ocean Key Resort and Spa, offering stunning views of the harbor. This signature waterfront restaurant in downtown Key West provides a romantic dining experience with Latin American-style small plates. The menu features a fusion of Caribbean and Floridian flavors, known as conch fusion, with must-try dishes like blackened shrimp mac and cheese and crispy yellowtail snapper.
name: Hot Tin Roof Restaurant
address: 0 Duval St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Revered, longtime eatery offering Caribbean-American cuisine, ocean views & a wine bar.
detail_description: Louie's Backyard is a renowned restaurant in Key West, offering a blend of Caribbean and American cuisine with stunning ocean views. For over 30 years, it has been serving an ever-changing menu featuring locally sourced seafood, meats, fruits, and vegetables. The restaurant's emphasis on showcasing Key West seafood is evident in dishes like conch chowder, baby octopus, rock shrimp, and fresh fish.
name: Louie's Backyard
address: 700 Waddell Ave, Key West, FL 33040, USA

detail_description: Cuban Coffee Queen is a small caf√© and mobile operation with three locations in Key West, offering classic Cuban coffee drinks and snacks. It's conveniently situated near the marina, making it a great stop for coffee and snacks before heading to Dry Tortugas National Park. The cafe serves expertly prepared Cafe Con Leche, best enjoyed with a traditional side of pan Cubano, a buttered and toasted piece of Cuban bread.
name: Cuban Coffee Queen
address: 291 Front St #6, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Seafood-focused American eatery set in an 1884 house with wraparound balconies for people-watching.
detail_description: Bagatelle is a charming American restaurant located in an 1884 house on Duval Street. The eatery offers a seafood-focused menu and is known for its famous brunch served all day, featuring traditional breakfast and luncheon dishes. The historic property exudes charm and intimacy, with two rooms available for private events.
name: Bagatelle
address: 115 Duval St #6505, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Mediterranean spot serving breakfast, lunch & dinner in a tranquil indoor space or outdoor terrace.
detail_description: Azur Restaurant, located in Old Town Key West, offers a tranquil indoor space and outdoor terrace where you can enjoy Mediterranean cuisine for breakfast, lunch, and dinner. The restaurant is known for its delicious brunches featuring a variety of innovative dishes alongside classic breakfast favorites. The menu includes twists on the classic Benedict, Italian-inspired breakfast carbonara, and a selection of unusual sandwiches, salads, and frittatas.
name: Azur Restaurant
address: 425 Grinnell St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Conch & Caribbean-style eats star at this laid-back eatery overlooking the seaport & marina.
detail_description: Conch Republic Seafood Company is a popular Key West restaurant known for its laid-back atmosphere and stunning waterfront views. The eatery offers a diverse menu featuring Caribbean-style seafood dishes, including options for vegans and vegetarians. Guests can enjoy live music performances while dining and taking in the sunset over the ocean. The restaurant's location pays homage to Key West's conch industry history, with the area once being known for its abundance of queen conchs.
name: Conch Republic Seafood Company
address: 631 Greene St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Chill spot adorned with local art serving globally inspired veggie & seafood eats, plus beer & wine.
detail_description: The Cafe is a vibrant and colorful eatery located in Key West, offering a diverse menu that caters to various dietary preferences. The cafe is adorned with local artwork and features a corrugated-tin-fronted counter, creating a trendy and inviting atmosphere. Whether you're a vegetarian, vegan, or have specific food allergies, The Cafe has something for everyone.
name: The Cafe
address: 509 Southard St #6835, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Eatery serving homemade pastas & other Italian classics in quarters with island-inspired decor.
detail_description: Mangia Mangia is an Italian eatery located in the heart of Old Town, offering a menu filled with delicious homemade pastas and other classic Italian dishes. The restaurant's island-inspired decor creates a unique dining atmosphere. While some of their dishes may lean towards the fancier side, such as the lobster linguine, there are also more affordable options like the standard meat sauce or tomato-based seafood sauces with scallops, conch, and mahi-mahi.
name: Mangia Mangia
address: 900 Southard St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: American cafe serving po' boys, conch fritters & the like in a circa-1838 house with outdoor seats.
detail_description: Caroline's Cafe is a charming American eatery located on Duval Street in Key West, housed in a historic building dating back to 1838. The cafe offers a diverse menu featuring traditional American fare like sandwiches, as well as specialty dishes such as jerk chicken and jambalaya. Visitors can enjoy outdoor seating while indulging in delicious meals like the Chicken Broccolini, Jerk Chicken, and Shrimp Po'Boy.
name: Caroline's Cafe
address: 310 Duval St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Hopping hot spot with Day of the Dead decor & a menu of Mexican street food & gluten-free beers.
detail_description: Amigos Tortilla Bar is a vibrant Mexican eatery in Key West, featuring Day of the Dead decor and a menu filled with Mexican street food and gluten-free beers. Despite its name, it's not a bar but rather a cozy spot offering mouthwatering fresh-Mex dishes. Located just off Duval Street, it provides indoor seating as well as an open-air counter for prime people-watching.
name: Amigos Tortilla Bar
address: 425 Greene St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: American fare & house brews in a chill, aviation-themed space with a courtyard shaded by palm trees.
detail_description: First Flight Island Restaurant & Brewery is a laid-back spot with an aviation theme and a courtyard shaded by palm trees. Situated at the historic location where Pan American World Airways was born, it's also home to the Southernmost Brewery in the States. The restaurant offers American cuisine and house-brewed beers crafted by Brewmaster Andrew Koennecke. The outdoor patio exudes island charm, offering a perfect setting to savor their popular street corn and avocado bowl.
name: First Flight Island Restaurant & Brewery
address: 301 Whitehead St, Key West, FL 33040, USA

excerpt: Relaxed dockside seafood eatery at the Ocean Key Resort & Spa with water views, drinks & live music.
detail_description: Sunset Pier is a vibrant and colorful dockside seafood eatery located at the Ocean Key Resort & Spa in Key West. It offers stunning water views, live music, and a relaxed atmosphere for enjoying mouth-watering tropical cuisines and drinks directly on the pier. The pier is known for serving Key West seafood classics like conch fritters and crab cakes, as well as Cuban cuisine.
name: Sunset Pier
address: 0 Duval St, Key West, FL 33040, USA
